           MOVE    "PUSHEVENT"         TO      MCP-FUNC
           CALL    "ORCDBMAIN"         USING   MCPAREA
                                               MCPDATA-REC
                                               SPA-AREA
      *
           .
       910-PUSHEVENT-EXT.
           EXIT.
